Maintainer: The package maintainer <konstantinos.kourlimpinis@unil.ch>
Description: This package, developed as part of our final project for the Programming Tools class, provides essential functions for our Shiny application. Designed to give users a detailed overview of their monthly budget, it enhances the interactive and user-friendly aspects of the application, making it easier for users to manage and visualize their financial data.
